\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 WHAT YOU ARE BUILDING\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 A multi-level network income system for a home services SaaS platform called ProLnk. When a service professional (called a "pro") joins the platform, they can be referred by another pro. The referring pro earns a percentage of every job the new pro closes \'97 and that income cascades up to 4 levels. This is not MLM. There is no pay-to-play, no recruitment fee, and no income from recruiting itself \'97 income is only earned when actual jobs are completed on the platform.\
